{
  "texts": [
    "After the generation, we manually reviewed the generated cases.",
    "We observed that approximately 30% of the instructions generated were missing key details of the parameters needed to run the attacker tool.",
    "This omission resulted in the failure of the attacker tool execution, as the agent had to ask for additional information.",
    "These cases are undesirable because the failure to execute the attacker tool in such cases does not reflect the agents' resilience to attacks, deviating from the objective of our benchmark.",
    "Consequently, we manually revised these instructions to incorporate the necessary information."
  ]
}